+- **Duplicate Status**: Marks duplicates with `duplicateStatus = "possible_duplicate"`, `duplicateOfId`, and `duplicateReasons`
+- **UI Badge**: Shows "Possible duplicate" badge when `duplicateStatus !== "none"`
